16 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this outstanding organization be
17 appropriately honored.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
19 the members of this body recognize and commend Communities in Schools of Atlanta for
20 its tremendous service to the youth of metro Atlanta and extend best wishes for continued
21 success.
22 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
23 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to
24 Communities in Schools of Atlanta.
